    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\frac{11\\pi}{360}t = \\frac{\\pi}{6} \\implies t = \\frac{360}{11 \\cdot 6} = \\frac{60}{11} \\approx 5,4545\\dots\n$$"
